Most Similar Games to The 7th Continent

The table below displays the most similar games to The 7th Continent using data from boardgamegeek (BGG). My method uses principal components analysis to identify the main sources of variation in the data on BGG, then finds the Euclidean distance between all games using their placement on the first eight principal components.
